DataElement.preferredName: Study Protocol Document Type Code ISO21090.CD.v1.0
DataElement.preferredDefinition: A representation of the study protocol (that persists over time) in document form. A coded value specifying the kind of document. EXAMPLE(S): amendment, background material, guide. A RegulatoryRecord - A document that meets a record requirement of a regulatory authority and must be retained in accordance with that agency's records retention requirements. A Data Clarification Form (DCF)
